alHealthDay\"><strong>#WorldMentalHealthDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/girl-child-day\">International Day of the Girl Child</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DayOfTheGirl\">#DayOfTheGirl</a><br />\n11: <a href=\"https://www.hrc.org/campaigns/national-coming-out-day#coming-out-resources\">Coming Out Day</a></strong> <strong>\u00a0\u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ComingOutDay&amp;src=typed_query\">#ComingOutDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23NCOD\"><br />\n</a><strong>12:\u00a0<a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-arthritis-day/\">World Arthritis Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldArthritisDay\"><strong>#WorldArthritisDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>13: <a href=\"https://www.worldthrombosisday.org/\">World Thrombosis Day</a> \u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldThrombosisDay\"><span class=\"r-18u37iz\">#WorldThrombosisDay</span></a><br />\n</strong><strong>16: <a href=\"http://www.fao.org/world-food-day\">World Food Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldFoodDay\">#WorldFoodDay<br />\n</a>16:\u00a0<a href=\"https://globalcatday.org/\" rel=\"noopener\">Global Cat Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23globalcatday&amp;src=typed_query\" rel=\"noopener\">#GlobalCatDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldArthritisDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>17: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/day-for-eradicating-poverty\">International Day for the Eradication of Poverty</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EndPovertyDay\">#EndPoveryDay<br />\n</a>19: <a href=\"https://www.worldvaluesday.com/\">World Values Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldValuesDay\">#WorldValuesDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>29: <a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/national-internet-day/\">National Internet Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldInternetDay&amp;src=typed_query\">#WorldInternetDay</a> (Internationally recognized)<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldInternetDay\"><br />\n</a>31:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/cities-day\">World Cities Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldCitiesDay\">#WorldCitiesDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2><strong>November</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3: <a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/biosphere-reserves\">International Day for Biosphere Reserves</a>\u00a0\u2014 <a class=\"css-4rbku5 css-18t94o4 css-901oao css-16my406 r-1cvl2hr r-1loqt21 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0\" dir=\"ltr\" role=\"link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BiosphereReserves?src=hashtag_click\">#BiosphereReserves</a><br />\n13:\u00a0<a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-kindness-day/\">World Kindness Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldKindnessDay\">#WorldKindnessDay</a><br />\n14:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worlddiabetesday.org/\">World Diabetes Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldDiabetesDay\"><strong>#WorldDiabetesDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>16: <a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/toleranceday\">International Day for Tolerance\u00a0</a>\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ToleranceDay\"><strong>#ToleranceDay</strong></a><br />\n<strong>19:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldtoiletday.info/\">World Toilet Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldToiletDay\">#WorldToiletDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldDiabetesDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>20: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-childrens-day\">World Children\u2019s Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldChildrensDay\">#WorldChildrensDay</a><br />\n21: <a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-pancreatic-cancer-day/\">World Pancreatic Cancer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPancreaticCancerDay\">#WorldPancreaticCancerDay</a><br />\n21: <a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-philosophy-day/#:~:text=We%20celebrate%20World%20Philosophy%20Day,occurred%20on%20November%2021%2C%202002.\">World Philosophy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPhilosophyDay\">#WorldPhilosophyDay</a></strong><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-television-day\">World Television Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldTVDay\">#WorldTVDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23ChildrensDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>25:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/endviolenceday/\">International Day for the Elimination of Violence Against Women</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EndViolenceAgainstWomen\">#EndViolenceAgainstWomen</a><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2>December</h2>\n<p><strong>1: <a href=\"https://www.unaids.org/en/World_AIDS_Day\">World AIDS Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldAIDSDay\">#WorldAIDSDay</a><br />\n3: <a href=\"http://givingtuesday.org/\">Giving Tuesday</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GivingTuesday\">#GivingTuesday</a><br />\n3:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.idpwd.com.au/\">International Day of People with Disabilities</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IDPwD24\">#IDPwD24</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPWD\"><br />\n</a><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/volunteer-day\">International Volunteer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/VolunteerDay\">#VolunteerDay<br />\n</a>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-soil-day\">World Soil Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldSoilDay\">#WorldSoilDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IVD2014\"><br />\n</a><strong>9:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/anti-corruption-day\">International Anti-Corruption Day\u00a0</a>\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AntiCorruptionDay\">#AntiCorruptionDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/humanrightsday\">International Human Rights Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HumanRightsDay\">#HumanRightsDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/mountain-day\">International Mountain Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MountainDay\">#MountainDay<br />\n</a>18:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/migrants-day\">International Migrants Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MigrantsDay\">#MigrantsDay</a></strong></p>\n<div style=\"background-color: #8362ae; padding: 4px;\"></div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #efebeb; padding: 5px;\">\n<h2><strong> \u25ba </strong><b>About the Author</b></h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #efebeb; padding: 5px;\"><a style=\"color: #8362ae;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a> is the founder and editor-in-chief of Nonprofit Tech for Good. Fueled by a strong passion for the Internet, Heather spends her days (and some nights) helping nonprofits worldwide utilize digital marketing and fundraising tools for social good.</div>\n<hr />\n<p>Our <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Certificate in Social Media Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a> program covers the fundamentals of social media marketing and fundraising for your nonprofit. Participants will learn how to create a social media strategy, how to craft a content marketing plan, and current best practices for using social media for community engagement and fundraising.</p>\n<p>The program requires the completion of three webinars and costs $100 USD. To earn the 2024 certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both. <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Learn more &amp; register</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-37646 size-full aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C604&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&gt;</p>\n<hr />\n",
